ComicInfo.Summary:
With Violet captured and taken to Wonderland, Calie must once again journey to the realm of dreams gone mad to save her daughter from the diabolical clutches of the Duchess. But the Duchess isn't the only being standing in Callie's way as Wonderland is only more than happy to show her that its' revenge...is only beginning.
